text: Kishan Chand Parwani is a Pakistani politician. He has served as the member of the National Assembly of Pakistan. == Political career == He won the National Assembly of Pakistan seat for minorities on the ticket of Pakistan Muslim League (Q) in the Pakistani general election, 2008. == References == Category:Politicians from Sindh Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Kishan Chand Parwani
